<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Montserrat:500,800&display=swap&subset=cyrillic-ext" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Montserrat', 'Google Sans', 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Arial, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
      color: #5e6e82;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }
    .header-img, .footer-img {
      width: 592px;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .content {
      width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      /* text-align: left; */
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 21px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .footer-img{
      margin-top: 2%;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img class="header-img" src="cid:headerImage" alt="Header Image"> 
    <div class="content">
  <p><strong>Subject: Your Order Confirmation from <%= nameBusinessCode %></strong></p>
  <p>Hello <%= to %>,</p>
  <p>Thank you very much for your order from <%= nameBusinessCode %>! We are pleased to inform you that we have received your order, and it is currently being processed.</p>
  <p><strong>Order Details:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Order Date: <%= dateOrder %></li>
    <li>Order Number: <%= numOrder %></li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Shipping Details:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Recipient Name: <%= to %></li>
    <li>Shipping Address: <%= city %> <%= street %> <%= numBuild %></li>
  </ul>
  <p>We will send you another update once your order is on its way. If you have any further questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.</p>
  <p>Thank you for choosing <%= nameBusinessCode %>. We appreciate your trust in us and look forward to serving you again in the future.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br>
  The <%= nameBusinessCode %> Team</p>
</div>
<img class="footer-img" src="cid:footerImage" alt="Footer Image">
</div>
</body>
</html>
